    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh i didn't know about that. i thought aspirin was fine for everyone. i've actually given him a small dose before when he was younger and he was fine. is it really that dangerous if it's just a one-off thing to get the fever down quickly? he's really struggling right now.",
